!ศอออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออออผ
Function GetNPrice : double;
var
  nPrice, sSkid, spNDS : double;
{
  spNDS := SpStep.NDS;
  GetNPRice := 0;
  if (SpStep.kol = 0)
    Exit;
  if (BaseDoc.VhodNal = 1)
    spNDS := 0;
  nPrice := SpStep.Price + (SpNDS / SpStep.Kol);

  // ชจคช ญ ฅคจญจๆใ 
  case SpStep.PrSkid of
    1: sSkid := SpStep.Price * SpStep.VlSkid / 100;  //แชจคช %
    2: sSkid := SpStep.VlSkid / SpStep.Kol;          //แชจคช แใฌฌ
    3: sSkid := SpStep.Price * SpStep.VlSkid / 100;  //แชจคช %
    4: sSkid := SpStep.VlSkid;                       //แชจคช แใฌฌ
  end;

  nPrice := nPrice - sSkid;
  if (BaseDoc.VHSkid = 1)
    nPrice := nPrice - (nPrice * BaseDoc.Skidka / 100)
  else
    nPrice := nPrice - ( SpStep.Kol*SpStep.Price + SpNDS - sSkid*SpStep.Kol)
                        / (BaseDoc.Total + BaseDoc.Skidka)
                        * BaseDoc.Skidka / SpStep.Kol;
  GetNPrice := nPrice;
}
